Hellenic Said to Buy a Cargo of Azeri Light Crude From Chevron

-- B y   S h e r r y   S u
-- 
2011-06-03T14:30:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-03/hellenic-said-to-buy-a-cargo-of-azeri-light-crude-from-chevron.html
Hellenic Petroleum SA,  Greece ’s
biggest refiner, bought 80,000 metric tons of Azeri Light crude
from Chevron Corp., according to two traders who participate in
the market.  The cargo is for loading June 25 to July 5 from the Turkish
port of Ceyhan in the Mediterranean, said the people, who
declined to be identified because they aren’t authorized to
speak on the matter.  Details of the sale are as follows:  To contact the reporter on this story:
